headline: Werner® Wins Prestigious Lee Anderson Veteran and Military Spouse Employment Award From Hiring Our Heroes
summary: OMAHA, Neb., November 21, 2025--Werner Enterprises, Inc. (Nasdaq: WERN), a premier transportation and logistics provider, proudly announced it has been honored with the distinguished Lee Anderson Veteran and Military Spouse Employment Award, presented by the U.S. Chamber of Commerce Foundation's Hiring Our Heroes initiative.
